# Per-run output folders are named after release_name and live under --task-dir
# (kept outside this repo by default). If you ever run inside the repo, ignore them too.

# NOTE: tools/probe/trace_processor_shell is committed ON PURPOSE (bundled binary
# to avoid flaky runtime downloads). It is NOT ignored. Make sure the committed
# file is the right platform build (Linux x86-64 for Hygon/NV servers).
